      • execute

        public cn.hutool.json.JSONObject execute(cn.hutool.http.Method method,
                                         String url,
                                         cn.hutool.json.JSONObject body)
        Execute a HTTP request.
        Parameters:
        method - The HTTP method.
        url - The URL to request.
        body - The body of the request (if any).
        Returns:
        The response JSON object. Null if no response body was returned.
        Throws:
        GuildedException - If Guilded returns an error.
        HttpRequestException - if an error occurred while sending HTTP request.
